okay something is really

00:43:33.279 --> 00:43:36.730
screwed up with velocities.
What is velocity?

00:43:36.730 --> 00:43:45.369
Velocity is space over
time--miles per hour.

00:43:45.369 --> 00:43:50.039
Therefore--so,
space and time are messed up

00:43:50.039 --> 00:43:54.820
when you get close to the speed
of light.

